Package: agendacodeR
Title: Naive Bayes multiclass classification of Policy Agendas data
Version: 0.2
Author: Matt W. Loftis
Maintainer: Matt W. Loftis <mattwloftis@ps.au.dk>
Description: Implement multiclass Naive Bayes classifier and provide various associated tools.
    This package is useful for applying and validating automated codings to policy agendas data.
